description.narrative: At the community and municipal level, UNICEF was able to extend coverage of child protection systems from 135 to 155 municipalities (out of a total of 340), and increased areas of intervention from 104 to 247 communities.; In addition, the programme worked on the issue of child protection against violence, together with faith-based organisations and community radios in 12 of Guatemala’s departments. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/01/2022
